oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:title: St. Vincent DePaul Church Job No. 16613
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:subject: Accounting; Hatch Show Print (Firm);
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:description: Typed purchase order form for St. Vincent DePaul Church. Receipt indicates agreed price, size, order quantity, shipping location and description for two poster orders: the first features a Summer Workshop on June 23, and the second, a concert at the Nashville War Memorial on June 29. To view the posters for this order see https://digi.countrymusichalloffame.org/digital/collection/hatch3/id/32620 and https://digi.countrymusichalloffame.org/digital/collection/hatch3/id/32618.
